<span class="item">
                        	<h1 class="fn">Perfect Guacamole</h1>
</span>
                        	<div class="entry-meta">
								
                            	
                                	<p>Posted by Elise on May  5, 2009</p>
                            	
                            	<p>Filed under <a href="http://www.simplyrecipes.com/recipes/all_seasons/">All Seasons</a>, <a href="http://www.simplyrecipes.com/recipes/appetizer/">Appetizer</a>, <a href="http://www.simplyrecipes.com/recipes/condiment/">Condiment</a>, <a href="http://www.simplyrecipes.com/recipes/gluten-free/">Gluten-Free</a>, <a href="http://www.simplyrecipes.com/recipes/low_carb/">Low Carb</a>, <a href="http://www.simplyrecipes.com/recipes/mexican_and_tex_mex/">Mexican and Tex Mex</a>, <a href="http://www.simplyrecipes.com/recipes/quick/">Quick</a>, <a href="http://www.simplyrecipes.com/recipes/side_dish/">Side Dish</a>, <a href="http://www.simplyrecipes.com/recipes/snack/">Snack</a></p>
