								<p>Southern California girl here and I agree, add the garlic and for some reason a splash, and I mean a splash, of vinegar adds something, not sure why but my college roommate taught that and her people were from (no kidding) Chihuahua Mexico...<br />
Don't forget to save a pit from the avocado for any leftovers.  If you put it in the leftovers, they don't seem to brown as bad...</p>	
